\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 9. Permission & Access Control Matrix\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 9.1 Permission Resolution Order\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0\fs26 \cf0 1. Check user is authenticated (JWT valid, not expired)\
2. Check tenant_id matches resource tenant (RLS)\
3. Check user's org-level role\
4. Check user's aircraft-level access record\
5. Check user's book-level permission within that aircraft access\
6. Allow or deny\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

