\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 15.4 Access Revocation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 When an owner revokes a mechanic's aircraft access:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs26 \cf0 1. aircraft_access.status = "revoked"\
2. aircraft_access.revoked_at = now()\
3. aircraft_access.revoked_by_id = owner_user_id\
4. Mechanic immediately loses aircraft from their dashboard (next API call)\
5. All active sessions invalidated for that resource (cache cleared)\
6. Mechanic receives: "Your access to N1234X has been revoked."\
7. Audit log entry created\
8. All DRAFT entries by mechanic flagged: 
\f5 \uc0\u9888 \u65039 
\f4  "Access revoked \'97 entry incomplete"\
9. All SIGNED entries remain intact (FAA requires permanence)\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

